{3: 'As the night sky fades, the first rays of dawn peek over the horizon.'}
{1: 'RImgBg1DisableSlow'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory664.jpg'}
{3: 'Under the watchful eyes of the Purifying Force and Scarab, the Ascendants escort Luna toward the Inver-Hetero Tower.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Bianca', 3: "We've reassigned everyone who saw the agent. We need to keep this quiet.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "Bunching up here will turn heads. We'll cover the other Ascendants while they clear out.", 4: '1'}
{2: "I'm counting on you, Bianca.", 3: '11'}
{3: 'Bianca shoots Luna a worried look but moves aside to let her pass.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Luna', 3: "If this goes as planned, it'll be the final step.", 4: '1'}
{2: "Just to be clear, is Selene the only one you're after?", 3: '16'}
{2: 'Luna', 3: "I can't make any promises. Even I don't know what's inside that tower.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Luna', 3: "But as I said, I hope this isn't our last collaboration.", 4: '1'}
{3: 'She speaks with absolute certainty.'}
{3: 'Any more questions would be pointless. None of the human factions have figured out how to safely explore the Inver-Hetero Tower.'}
{3: 'A little hope is better than certain death.'}
{3: 'No one else speaks. Luna turns and bids Alpha goodbye with a wistful smile.'}
{2: 'Luna', 3: 'See you soon then.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 3: 'Alpha remains silent, her nod the only farewell she offers.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Luna', 3: 'You too, 【kuroname】.', 4: '1'}
{3: 'She adds with a mischievous grin.'}
